    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions within 15% of experimental hemolysis measurements across all 5 operating points. RH < 1 confirmed at worst-case condition. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements. The computational model is deemed credible for supporting the regulatory decision regarding CPB device hemolysis tolerance assessment.",
